requirements.txt.description: Python dependencies file with 9 packages: ib_async (IB API), river (online ML), dash/plotly/dash-bootstrap-components (dashboard), pandas/numpy (data), pandas_market_calendars (exchange calendars), aiohttp (async HTTP)

config.py.description: Dynamic configuration module using dataclass with environment variable support. Uses get_config() singleton pattern. Default values: IB_HOST=127.0.0.1, IB_PORT=7497, IB_CLIENT_ID=1, DASHBOARD_PORT=8050. All settings can be overridden via environment variables.
